                Grays Harbor including: McCleary, Elma, Montesano, Central Park, Aberdeen, 
                Cosmopolis and Hoquiam.  Our regular meeting time is at 6pm on Wednesday evenings, 
                in the lower level of Montesano Church of God on Spruce Street.  The troop meets 
                September through early June, taking a break from regular activities during the 
                summer and school breaks.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our Girl Scout Troop spans from Daisies (Kindergarten) through Ambassadors (High School Seniors) 
                and everything in between.  Each level meets separately, but we have special meeting nights 
                and activities throughout the year for the full troop.  Our special troop dynamic fosters a 
                family atmosphere with scouts forming bonds with other scouts in different levels.
            </p>
            <p>
